oai_dc:dc.dc:title: THE ESTUARIES OF NATAL: A METHOD OF CLASSIFICATION
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Perry, J.E.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: classification method
estuary
Natal
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This poster paper describes a .hydrological/hydraulic classification of the estuaries of Natal, based upon aerial photography. The modus operandi is outlined and although the study is in its early stages, some key factors (natural and man-made) are indicated together with the method by which they are quantified.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 18 (1982): Proceedings of 18th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Cape Town, South Africa, 1982.; 137
